<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원 정보 수정 - Refresh Beverage Mall</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            margin: 0; padding: 40px;
            background-color: #f8fafc; color: #334155;
        }
        .edit-container {
            max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white;
            padding: 35px; border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b;
            margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 5px solid #4b5563; padding-left: 12px;
        }
        .info-msg {
            background-color: #f1f5f9; padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        label {
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #475569;
            display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        input[type="text"], input[type="password"], input[type="email"] {
            width: 100%; padding: 12px; font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 6px;
            box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.2s; background-color: #fff;
        }
        input:focus {
            outline: none; border-color: #4b5563;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.1);
        }
        .static-username {
            background-color: #f8fafc; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: bold; cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        .form-actions {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .btn-submit {
            background-color: #4b5563; color: white; border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover { background-color: #374151; }
        .btn-back { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
        .btn-back:hover { color: #1e293b; text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="edit-container">
    <h2>👤 회원 정보 수정</h2>
    <div class="info-msg">변경할 항목만 입력해 주세요. 비밀번호를 빈칸으로 두면 기존 비밀번호가 유지됩니다.</div>

    <form action="" method="POST">
        <label>아이디 (변경 불가)</label>
        <input type="text" class="static-username" value="<%= user.username %>" readonly>

        <label for="name">이름</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="<%= user.name %>" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요">

        <label for="password">새 비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="변경할 경우에만 입력하세요">

        <label for="birth">생년월일</label>
        <input type="text" id="birth" name="birth" value="<%= user.birth || '' %>" placeholder="예: 2000-01-01">

        <label for="address">주소지</label>
        <input type="text" id="address" name="address" value="<%= user.address || '' %>" placeholder="주소를 입력하세요">

        <label for="phone">연락처</label>
        <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" value="<%= user.phone || '' %>" placeholder="예: 010-1234-5678">

        <label for="email">이메일</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" value="<%= user.email || '' %>" placeholder="이메일을 입력하세요">

        <div class="form-actions">
            <a href="../mypage" class="btn-back">← 마이페이지로 돌아가기</a>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">수정 완료</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>